Like let=E2=80=99s say you have a pot of money and you want to start lendin=
g it directly=C2=A0to private equity sponsors to finance leveraged buyouts.=
 How do you start=3F Probably you hire some former bankers with good relati=
onships and have them call on private equity sponsors, saying =E2=80=9Chi, =
we=E2=80=99d like to lend you money to finance your buyouts.=E2=80=9D The s=
ponsors are like =E2=80=9CSure, we can always use more money. Honestly we h=
