ing=C2=A0<em>against=C2=A0</em>the market move. When stocks go up, 60/40 in=
vestors are overweight stocks, so they sell stocks, etc.</p> <p style=3D"ma=
rgin: 16px 0;">If this were true, you might try to profit from it. =E2=80=
